{"tid":904782,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"今年算唔算近十年華語電影最全盛既一年","createTime":"2018-11-16T15:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T06:58:23.000Z","uid":222425,"like":5,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c8a6f0ea6d0a55119a3dbb3a1d9f8c395fe8dd1d","tid":904782,"uid":222425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:39:24.000Z","msg":"今年真係好多高質華語片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇下金馬奬最佳導演個提名就知<br />\n<br />\n張藝謀 - 影<br />\n畢贛 - 地球最後的夜晚<br />\n姜文- 邪不壓正<br />\n萬瑪才旦 - 撞死了一隻羊<br />\n婁燁- 風中有朵雨做的雲<br />\n<br />\n國師張藝謀回歸之作，將水墨畫影像化，鏡頭靚到癲，唯美至極。<br />\n<br />\n30歲未夠既天才導演畢贛 第2套劇情長片就提名最佳導演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，套戲我未睇但聽聞有個50分鐘3D長鏡頭令人嘆為觀止，Cannes好評如潮<br />\n<br />\n婁燁不嬲高質上套推拿已經拎過最佳劇情片，今次回歸懸疑題材又係令人值得期待。<br />\n<br />\n仲有大象席地而坐呢套更加要respect , 導演處女作成為遺作(RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ), 仲有姜文邪不壓正，岩井俊二既你好之華，無入圍既無雙。<br />\n<br />\n真心今年華語電影真係爆曬seed <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  荷里活反而今年無乜好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be441998e30a23b0e779f0cb4f218490f1b9bc1","tid":904782,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"比較係百花齊放咁解 <br />\n<br />\n但一定唔係最頂盛"},{"pid":"918f005b9e7d2e859151b4a5375e7ee1439363e1","tid":904782,"uid":77788,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:52:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00223de3aa521f2892625021f34cd825a8815a27","tid":904782,"uid":183612,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:54:37.000Z","msg":"點解會無 無雙<br />\n我覺得做得幾好"},{"pid":"8b2315b86d853cf8441826ff743331764780d7c1","tid":904782,"uid":222425,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"918f005b9e7d2e859151b4a5375e7ee1439363e1","tid":904782,"uid